Definition: in a grotesque manner
Example: behind the house lay two nude figures grotesquely bald, with deliberate knife-slashes marking their bodies
Synonyms: adj, all, ugly, grotesque, monstrously, monstrous, in, a, manner, behind, the, house, lay, two, nude, figures, bald, with, deliberate, knife-slashes, marking, their, bodies
Category: adv.all
